cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and sentiment analysis. The use of neural network architectures such as LSTM and CNN also suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves extracting trends from data, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the use of ensemble models suggests that it could also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
